<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q19_v2" title="Q19_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>
        Una cuerda mide 
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        metros. Se fabrica otra cuerda que tiene el doble de esa longitud. En la etiqueta se escribe la expresión que representa la longitud de la nueva cuerda. 
        ¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones puede corresponder a esa etiqueta?
      </qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La nueva cuerda mide el doble de <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, esta expresión sí puede corresponder a la etiqueta.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>6</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El doble de la longitud original es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. Además, si se compara con esta opción, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:msup><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>16</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>48</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, esta opción no representa la nueva longitud.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>12</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El doble de la longitud original es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>. En cambio, <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msqrt><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mrow></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>, que corresponde a la longitud original, no al doble. Por eso esta opción no puede ser la etiqueta.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>8</m:mn>
            <m:msqrt>
              <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            </m:msqrt>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El doble de <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. De hecho, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>, por lo que esta expresión representa cuatro veces la longitud original, no el doble.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la longitud original</strong></p>
            <p>La cuerda original mide <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> metros.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular el doble de esa longitud</strong></p>
            <p>Tener el doble significa multiplicar por <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, la nueva cuerda mide <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> metros.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p><em>Opción A:</em> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Coincide exactamente con el resultado obtenido.</p>
            <p><em>Opción B:</em> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. No coincide con <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p><em>Opción C:</em> <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> y <m:math><m:mrow><m:msqrt><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:msqrt><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>, así que corresponde a la longitud original, no al doble.</p>
            <p><em>Opción D:</em> <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>8</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>. Es mayor que <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math> y no coincide con el doble pedido.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La expresión que puede corresponder a la etiqueta de la nueva cuerda es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:msqrt><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:msqrt></m:mrow></m:math>, es decir, la alternativa A.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>